data.description: Gorgeous Townhouse, Three story. The main floor is bright and open where the kitchen connects to the deck and overlooks the casual dining and gathering room. Kitchen features white cabinetry with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances with gas cooking. The top floor features the owner's suite with a spa like bathroom offering a large shower, dual vanities and a large walk in closet, and a secondary bedroom with its private bathroom. Downstairs you'll find another bedroom with its own private bathroom and the 2 car garage. Devon park is a charming community, it has a Dog Park!! it's only 2.6 miles from the I-85. Don't miss this one! schedule your showing today!
